{"tid":971773,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【鏗鏘透視檔案】戒丁幾耐先健康 原來唐代醫師已經有講？","createTime":"2019-01-07T01:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T13:19:57.000Z","uid":43231,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b25df466836e5b6c140bac009f4f2c4deced281f","tid":971773,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"「戒丁」，經常為討論區熱門的話題，但究竟要戒多久的時間，身體才會好轉呢？是次我們就邀請到丁齡超過十年的丁生，去嘗試戒丁一星期，再由徐澤昌醫師去診斷身體有否改善，再由醫師分享一下相關的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZebaQ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZebaQ7.png&h=793a7573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">醫師更提到早在唐代已有「行房頻率」的參考。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO6tc40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO6tc40.png&h=728a8b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">徐澤昌醫師指出中醫並不主張禁慾，正常的性生活其實對人體健康有幫助。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190107/59105280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F59105280&d=s24fVcVkFUhXJeusUnrbXbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8ff5c27c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F59105280&h=93d27d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190107/59105280</a>"},{"pid":"10bda7b068055198348257fc4373822341ed8f12","tid":971773,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:48:45.000Z","msg":"蕭別離召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8336fe8a9e46b87f64f18ad159dca6bcb3d5ff46","tid":971773,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"丁生 一位平凡既打工仔<br />\n日頭就打工 夜晚就打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm